Detailed Description

cvmx_ciu2_msired_pp::_ip2

CIU2_MSIRED_PPX_IPx (Pass 2) Contains reduced MSI interrupt numbers for delivery to software. Note MSIRED delivery can only be made to PPs, not to IO; thus there are no CIU2_MSIRED_IO registers.
